casebody.data:
The State of Ohio, Appellee, v. White, Appellant.

[Cite as State v. White (1995), 73 Ohio St.3d 348.]

(No. 95-429 Submitted May 9, 1995 Decided August 23, 1995.) Michael T. White, pro se. Per Curiam.

We affirm the judgment of the court of appeals for the reasons stated in its opinion.

Judgment affirmed.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas, Wright, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer and Cook, JJ., concur.
